text: St. Elsewhere is an American medical drama television series. It was created by Joshua Brand and John Falsey, and it orignally aired from October 26, 1982 to May 24, 1988 on NBC. ==Other websites== * Category:NBC network series Category:English-language television programs Category:1982 American television series debuts Category:1988 American television series endings Category:American medical television series
